      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DASHING DONNA (1) was fast into stride from box six to score two back (22.50) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 5th at this track (22.50). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. LEKTRA AELA (7) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 390m behind Paw Xanthie (22.58) in a Grade 5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has ability and can measure up. PAW UCARTY (2) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at Geelong over 400m behind Shallow Sally (23.10) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. TRENTINO (8) was on the bunny all the way to win last start. Right in the mix again.",
